00:54:05.199 --> 00:54:14.000
kind of directly going into parts of the UI. So we're pulling that text out of the location data

00:54:14.000 --> 00:54:20.399
and putting it directly into the UI. So if we were to do that in the UI part of the application,

00:54:20.399 --> 00:54:24.399
so that's kind of static, we would have to be updating that manually.

00:54:25.360 --> 00:54:29.840
But yeah, so why we push it always to the server, or we prefer to push it to the server,

00:54:29.840 --> 00:54:36.719
is so that we can have access to, and it's not just the reactives as well, we can do,

00:54:36.719 --> 00:54:41.199
